@node Requirements
@title "What you need"

    Guess a Number has been tested (and worked) on:

       A500 w/ 2.1, 2.5 megs fast RAM, .5 megs chip RAM, HD
       A500 w/ 1.3, 2.5 megs fast RAM, .5 megs chip RAM, HD

       It should run fine on about any Amiga computer, just be
       sure to set your screen font to 8 points and the system font
       to 8 points (although I don't know if that makes a difference)
       and it should be fine.  If you have any trouble just @{"contact" link contact}
       me and let me know.
@endnode
